    featuredImagePrompt: "A wide-angle, slightly elevated perspective of a vibrant but organized student protest in an Indian city street. Focus on diverse young students holding signs that express concern over education and justice, some holding portraits of a young student (representing Vihaan, but stylized to avoid specific likeness). The mood is serious but determined. Prominent MNS flags or banners are visible, suggesting political backing. City buildings are in the background, subtly blurred. Emphasize dynamic composition and warm, hopeful lighting, avoiding anything overtly aggressive or somber. The scene should convey collective action and a call for change. Ensure the image stands out with a unique visual angle and color palette, different from typical protest stock photos.",
