    featuredImagePrompt: "A wide-angle, cinematic scene of a tense, modern financial district skyline at dusk. The cityscape should be imposing and somewhat ominous, with muted, cool colors dominated by greys and dark blues, occasionally broken by subtle, digital red lines or downward-trending crypto charts subtly integrated into the sky or reflected on glass skyscrapers. A sense of global uncertainty and financial tension should pervade the scene, without showing any explicit conflict or national symbols. The composition should suggest interconnectedness and scale, with a slightly distant, elevated perspective.",
