    featuredImagePrompt: "A dynamic, high-energy conceptual visual blending a football transfer announcement with a World Cup Final. On one side, a blurred figure in a Chelsea FC kit (representing Ethan Rogers) signing a contract, with a shimmering, almost futuristic glow around him. On the other side, a vibrant, packed football stadium with a large scoreboard showing 'SPAIN vs ARGENTINA - FIFA WORLD CUP FINAL 2026', with a blurred but ecstatic crowd. A subtle graphical overlay connects the two scenes, perhaps a timeline or a flowing ribbon, symbolizing the convergence of these major events. Emphasize motion, excitement, and a blend of club and international football elements. The color palette should be vibrant blues, whites, and the national colors of Spain and Argentina.",
