    outlook: "The immediate outlook for Bitcoin is a critical test of the $68,000 resistance. A successful breach could pave the way for further gains, while a rejection might lead to consolidation or a pullback. Ether appears to have a more bullish near-term outlook, with $2,100 as a tangible target, supported by fundamental demand. In the broader context, the trend of increasing regulatory oversight, exemplified by Pakistan\'s actions, is expected to continue globally. This will likely shape the market\'s structure, potentially increasing compliance costs but also offering greater legitimacy and stability in the long run. Overall, the market remains cautiously optimistic, but key technical levels and regulatory developments will be crucial determinants of its trajectory.",
