      neutralCase: "The crypto market will continue to exhibit a dual nature, with robust institutional interest in tokenization slowly building a bridge to traditional finance, while native crypto sectors like DeFi grapple with efficiency challenges. Bitcoin\'s price will remain volatile, influenced by a mix of speculative trading and macroeconomic developments, oscillating within established ranges. Tokenization will progress steadily but face ongoing regulatory and integration challenges, preventing rapid, transformative change in the short to medium term.",
