      neutralCase: "The crypto market will continue its volatile trajectory, balancing innovation with regulatory challenges. Stablecoins will see incremental adoption in specific use cases, while compliance standards will gradually improve. However, systemic risks, including geopolitical interference and security vulnerabilities, will persist, preventing a rapid, widespread institutional embrace.",
