    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual visual representing the dual nature of Artificial Intelligence\'s impact on financial markets. On one side, a gleaming, upward-trending stock chart intertwined with microchips and digital currency symbols, signifying growth and opportunity. On the other side, a fractured or glitching digital screen displaying a news headline with \'ERROR\' or \'MISINFORMATION\', overlaid with a subtle warning sign, symbolizing risks and inaccuracies. The background should subtly blend elements of a global financial city skyline and a neural network, with a clear separation or contrast between the \'opportunity\' and \'risk\' sides. Use a sophisticated, modern color palette with blues, greens, and subtle reds for contrast.",
