      neutralCase: "These events are part of the crypto market\'s ongoing evolution, representing growing pains rather than existential threats. While they expose weaknesses, they also spur innovation in security and compliance. The market\'s resilience has been tested before, suggesting it will absorb these incidents and continue its trajectory, albeit with heightened awareness of existing challenges.",
      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "A probability-weighted outlook suggests a \'Neutral to Mildly Bearish\' sentiment in the short term, leaning towards \'Neutral\' in the medium to long term. The immediate impact is a likely dip in trust, especially concerning AI-driven information and DeFi security. However, the industry\'s history of adapting to challenges, coupled with increasing regulatory attention, implies that these incidents will eventually lead to necessary improvements rather than a complete market collapse. Probability: Bearish (35%), Neutral (45%), Bullish (20%).",
