      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "A neutral-to-slightly-bearish outlook dominates the immediate term, with an estimated 50% probability of continued range-bound trading, 30% probability of further downside due to macro/geopolitical risks, and 20% probability of a bullish rebound if catalysts emerge. The key inflection points are the July US economic data and Fed decisions.",
