    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual visual representing the cryptocurrency market in a state of consolidation. Imagine a digital landscape with various crypto assets (subtly hinted at, e.g., abstract shapes representing Bitcoin and stablecoins) being compressed or settling. A prominent, slightly descending line graph (representing market cap or price) merges towards a strong, stable horizontal line (power law support). The scene should evoke a sense of quiet re-evaluation, with muted, intelligent lighting. Incorporate subtle elements suggesting liquidity outflow (e.g., faint digital streams moving away from a central pool) and the idea of \'accumulation\' (e.g., a subtle, glowing area around the support line). The overall aesthetic should be sophisticated, data-driven, and slightly futuristic, avoiding any generic stock photo feel.",
